hotkeys (0.1.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial release
  * Linux keyboard automation tool with GTK4 interface
  * 3x3 hotkey grid for numeric keypad navigation
  * Application-specific board configurations
  * Profile system for different workflows
  * Modifier key combinations support
  * X11 active window detection
  * Support for shortcuts, text input, and automation actions

